              Over a decade of building web properties, scaling organic traffic, and creating digital products. 
              Co-Founder at <span class="text-cream-100 font-semibold">Mindjek Technologies LLP</span>. Based in Kadi, Gujarat, India.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Status -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full mb-4 sm:mb-5 animate-fade-up border border-white/10" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 sm:w-2 sm:h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-cream-100 tracking-wide">Available for projects</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- CTAs -->
